		<title>Trained agents: perfect recipe for rewarding telemarketing outsourcing</title>
		<link>https://www.fusionbposervices.com/blog/telemarketing-outsourcing-3.html</link>
				<comments>https://www.fusionbposervices.com/blog/telemarketing-outsourcing-3.html#respond</comments>
				<pubDate>Wed, 14 Mar 2012 09:46:45 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Alicia Johnson]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Call Center]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[call center outsourcing]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[telemarketing outsourcing]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.fusionbposervices.com/blog/?p=4544</guid>
				<description><![CDATA[The business enterprises opt for telemarketing outsourcing to ensure that the investment on the marketing part of the business yields the desired returns. What makes the outsourced call centers so efficient in handling the marketing campaigns? Well it is the training they receive. And it is the trained agents solely that makes call center outsourcing [&#8230;]]]></description>
								<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a rel="&quot;lightbox&quot;&quot;" href="http://www.fusionbposervices.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/1-s2.0-S0304393206000985-gr1.jpg"><img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-4545" title="call center outsourcing" src="http://www.fusionbposervices.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/1-s2.0-S0304393206000985-gr1-300x198.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="198" srcset="https://www.fusionbposervices.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/1-s2.0-S0304393206000985-gr1-300x198.jpg 300w, https://www.fusionbposervices.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/1-s2.0-S0304393206000985-gr1.jpg 537w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></a>The business enterprises opt for telemarketing outsourcing to ensure that the investment on the marketing part of the business yields the desired returns. What makes the outsourced call centers so efficient in handling the marketing campaigns? Well it is the training they receive. And it is the trained agents solely that makes <strong><a title="call center outsourcing" href="http://www.fusionbposervices.com/ ">call center outsourcing</a></strong> such a rewarding option for the business firms.</p>
<p>Let us have a look at the various components of the training that are being organized in order to impart the agents with the required skills.</p>
<ul>
<li>As it has already been mentioned the primary aim of such training is to develop the necessary skills in the telemarketers and to enlighten them about the call center software and techniques. Also they are briefed about the market conditions as well as the various basic techniques of alluring targets.</li>
<li>How are these skills generated? Well they are made to handle sample calls and they are judged on the basis of how they handle the same. The first and foremost requirement is to be polite and maintain the cool no matter what the customer behavior is like.</li>
<li>Another important part of the training is that it teaches the agents as to how to handle customer rejections. It is not possible for the telemarketers to turn each and every sales call into an actual sales figure. Even one particular lead to be converted into sales needs a lot of follow up.</li>
</ul>
<p>Besides such training what becomes necessary on the part of the business investors is to arrange for pre campaign briefing sessions. These sessions are the best way to provide the external telemarketers with the relevant product or service information. Without such information a productive marketing strategy cannot be formulated.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
